{"tid":1844623,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[節錄多圖] 新技能GET！日本漁民學會了用美少女誘捕章魚","createTime":"2020-01-26T17:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T06:27:09.000Z","uid":15564,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ae1efe3f48320e500cc8eb16a21ae5c48539d722","tid":1844623,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:14:18.000Z","msg":"詳細source: <a href=\"https://www.techbang.com/posts/75793-japanese-fishermen-learn-to-trap-octopus-with-beautiful-girl?from=home_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techbang.com%2Fposts%2F75793-japanese-fishermen-learn-to-trap-octopus-with-beautiful-girl%3Ffrom%3Dhome_news&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=3cfeaa05\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.techbang.com/posts/75793-japanese-fishermen-learn-to-trap-octopus-with-beautiful-girl?from=home_news</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.techbang.com/system/images/543946/original/e1a3b48215f965d3f8a6be3df4c65175.gif?1579492081\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F543946%2Foriginal%2Fe1a3b48215f965d3f8a6be3df4c65175.gif%3F1579492081&h=0d122b52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.techbang.com/system/images/543960/original/ce2ccc891ce9303e1f94159c3ba99139.gif?1579492677\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F543960%2Foriginal%2Fce2ccc891ce9303e1f94159c3ba99139.gif%3F1579492677&h=17282573&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一步：設置死宅誘餌&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.techbang.com/system/images/543953/original/5cf406f01b7ab0895b837c5616b7fa02.jpg?1579492446\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F543953%2Foriginal%2F5cf406f01b7ab0895b837c5616b7fa02.jpg%3F1579492446&h=ff8b769b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二步：坐等死宅上鉤&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn0.techbang.com/system/images/543955/original/87aabdb9c48ce184c23cae557b71b826.jpg?1579492545\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn0.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F543955%2Foriginal%2F87aabdb9c48ce184c23cae557b71b826.jpg%3F1579492545&h=1baf1233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第三步：笑看死宅陌路&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.techbang.com/system/images/543956/original/4a7c7e52809df6a1c433c8181b16b9a5.jpg?1579492567\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F543956%2Foriginal%2F4a7c7e52809df6a1c433c8181b16b9a5.jpg%3F1579492567&h=c969bedf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大量屁股上長滿魚鉤的EVA小隊在等待被發配到海釣現場：<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.techbang.com/system/images/543958/original/5402948f058e96030c14efa53eeda867.jpg?1579492634\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F543958%2Foriginal%2F5402948f058e96030c14efa53eeda867.jpg%3F1579492634&h=ab525f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn0.techbang.com/system/images/543959/original/a3f9b3299a6042ceee8b99986adef03e.jpg?1579492657\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn0.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F543959%2Foriginal%2Fa3f9b3299a6042ceee8b99986adef03e.jpg%3F1579492657&h=16d8826c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「色誘章魚」科學原理</span><br />\n<br />\n一切到底是為什麼？<br />\n<br />\n我知道二次元小姐姐確實很有吸引力，但除了玄學領域，科學角度也應該有跡可循。確實，美色誘捕法的開創祖師爺小塚，在之前曾對這個現象的形成原理進行過一些經驗總結。他在自己的論壇裡說道：<br />\n<br />\n「我尋思這玩意能成功的原因，一是因為手辦的形狀跟甲殼類的肢體形狀很像（這是主要原因），二是因為我用的手辦誘餌都是跟螃蟹相似的紅色；再就是，章魚喜歡閃閃發光的東西。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>根據各類章魚科普資料可以歸納出，影響上鉤率的章魚形態喜好有三個方面：</strong><br />\n<br />\n生理捕食需求：喜歡紅色（源於蟹類顏色）和白色（源於貝類顏色）。<br />\n<br />\n生物本能特徵：好奇心強，看到形狀奇特、閃亮炫目的東西會想拿到爪裡抱一抱。<br />\n<br />\n嗜好：喜歡鑽各種孔洞，容器（因此有用瓶罐誘捕章魚的流派）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>好了，現在來看我們的小姐姐手辦，正好都符合相似的特徵&mdash;&mdash;</strong><br />\n<br />\n紅色+白色；<br />\n<br />\n形狀奇特（在章魚看來）；<br />\n<br />\n體態炫酷（在章魚看來）：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.techbang.com/system/images/543963/original/9a4eb0fe9cb7cae384dfbb5d02070b0d.jpg?1579492756\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F543963%2Foriginal%2F9a4eb0fe9cb7cae384dfbb5d02070b0d.jpg%3F1579492756&h=f5911f5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本文授權轉載遊研社： <a href=\"https://www.yystv.cn/p/6118\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yystv.cn%2Fp%2F6118&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=29e53e9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yystv.cn/p/6118</a>"},{"pid":"4cd497b4207e3e91e4c22e511bfa30ce06e1e9f1","tid":1844623,"uid":15564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:14:33.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a62ec1a90c2800c6cd5f50d1672785d86ec9e87","tid":1844623,"uid":153808,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:16:52.000Z","msg":"觸手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9f82e89485d21d3dc3ed19ceb09e354ccd3ecd","tid":1844623,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:18:47.000Z","msg":"真識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40336c022a4dbc02daffef50a146117f561d70a","tid":1844623,"uid":54878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:19:13.000Z","msg":"觸手play<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0fcca1b844d6ea7b424b74356a7241cc6f44ba","tid":1844623,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc59118777a89a97c02f69d54b21c735f508276","tid":1844623,"uid":165711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:25:01.000Z","msg":"喜歡鑽各種孔洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c7bcff200f96548ad7742c7d26888aacea468a","tid":1844